Prophet Ibrahim and the unknown history By Mr. Mahmoud Aalghemni (Arabic)

This book is a study of history trying to find out about the false relationship between prophet Abraham Palestine, put the light at the relationship the Prophet Abraham and the Egyptians, as well as access to real homeland of the Prophet Abraham and route of the real trips in the region.
